    "created_at": "2015-10-27T03:11:09Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-27T03:11:09Z",
    "body": "It seems that from Chrome 45 setting `page-visibility` doesn't prevent performance throttling any more, can you try using the `--disable-renderer-backgrounding` command line switch?\n\n``` js\napp.commandLine.appendSwitch(\"disable-renderer-backgrounding\");\n```\n\nRefs #2822.\n"
