    "updated_at": "2015-11-02T11:07:57Z",
    "body": "This flag is application-wide, you can append it before creating the test window so normal users won't be affected, but the windows created after that will still be affected though.\n\nFrom the source code the only way to prevent only one window being put into background is to keep playing audio in the page.\n"
