    "created_at": "2015-11-09T03:32:41Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-09T03:32:41Z",
    "body": "It seems that Chrome had [a bug](https://code.google.com/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=491895) that it doesn't update the background information immediately when audio starts/stops, and it got fixed very recently, I think we are hitting this bug. The `--disable-renderer-backgrounding` switch seems to be our only option.\n"
