    "created_at": "2015-11-23T08:22:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-11-23T08:22:46Z",
    "body": "The code that determines whether to lower the priority of renderer process is located at: https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/content/browser/renderer_host/render_process_host_impl.cc&sq=package:chromium&type=cs&l=2369\n\nAnd the `page-visibility` option is implemented at:\nhttps://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/atom/renderer/atom_renderer_client.cc#L207-L218\n\nI'm not sure from when it stops working in Chromium.\n"
